                                                            oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                                            oc:itemOrder 1 ;
                                                            oc:itemText "Show the full formula with **hyperlinked components** — each component must be an `<a href=\"#ref-N\">` link back to the appendix row for that raw data point. This is critical: the reader must be able to click through from the calculated value to each of its inputs." ],
